aphs of your damage output? Shouldn't you be posting graphs of damage done to you? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/umikar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mikar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 15<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/21/01 8:16:14 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: SoL: Combat Stability (Damage Mitigation)</span><hr size=1> The text talks about increasing the migitation by x%. One way to interpret this would be: <br>
